<plot>The past never dies. Akan finds out that one phone call is about to shatter his serene lifestyle in the United States. Suddenly the past meets the future as he has to relive the violent experiences of his Nigerian past. His membership in a brotherhood is exposed as well as the reason he joins them and the reason he might be running. Inspired by true events, Grey Focus shocks the viewer with it's blatant exposure of an ever increasing phenomenon in Nigerian University campuses.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?222979</url></doc>
